	(text "Did the math, realized I don't\nhave control system intuition.\n\nI have raw values I need to map to\nstardard resistor and capcitor size\nand values:\n- R_C = 14403.29218 Ω\n- C_C = 2.673 nF\n- C_P = 6.4152 pF\n\nThese are the values after \nplugging in a real output \ncap (CL21A226MAQNNN): \n- R_C = 10020.57613 Ω\n- C_C = 2.673 nF\n- C_P = 2.88684 pF\n\nThese are the standard \nvalues I'm going with:\n- R_C = 10 kΩ\n- C_C = 2.7 nF"
